title: Iowa's 48th Senate district
content:
The 48th District of the Iowa Senate is located in eastern Iowa, and is currently composed of Louisa County, as well as parts of Des Moines, Henry, and Muscatine counties.[1]

Dan Zumbach is the senator currently representing the 48th District.[2]
